CatDescriptText: The house was outfitted by William "Woogie" Harris, including the china cabinet and the figurines.Ira Vann and Lionel Harris are the sons of Charles "Teenie" Harris and Elsa Harris.
TitMainTitle: Ira Vann Harris, on left, with his brother, Lionel Harris wearing identical clothing, reaching over dining table, with round cake with two candles, in dining room of Charles "Teenie" Harris' house at 7604 Mulford Streetooden furniture, and large china cabinet in background
